# 8 Mika Hakkinen            1  20  Pitstop, out        0h02m14.033s pit 22.874
#30 Heinz-Harald Frentzen    1  21  Pitstop, out        0h02m31.318s pit 22.770
*39 Oliver Roberts           2   1  1:19.133 =1:19.133! 0h02m44.594s
